sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client<br/>(Prometheus, Dashboard)
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Upstream as Upstream Application<br/>8081/TCP HTTP localhost

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 1: Authenticated Proxy Request (Bearer Token)

    Client->>Proxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    activate Proxy

    Note over Proxy: Path Filter: check --ignore-paths

    Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authentication.k8s.io/v1/tokenreviews<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    activate K8sAPI
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: TokenReview response<br/>(authenticated user info, groups)
    deactivate K8sAPI

    Note over Proxy: Build SubjectAccessReview<br/>from config (Format1 or Format2)

    Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authorization.k8s.io/v1/subjectaccessreviews<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    activate K8sAPI
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview response<br/>(allowed: true/false)
    deactivate K8sAPI

    alt Authorized
        Note over Proxy: Inject x-remote-user,<br/>x-remote-groups headers
        Proxy->>Upstream: HTTP/8081 localhost<br/>+ x-remote-user headers<br/>No encryption (localhost)
        activate Upstream
        Upstream-->>Proxy: Response
        deactivate Upstream
        Proxy-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    else Denied
        Proxy-->>Client: 403 Forbidden<br/>(static error message)
    end

    deactivate Proxy

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 2: Metrics Scraping (Hardcoded Prometheus Allow)

    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(openshift-monitoring)<br/>SA: prometheus-k8s

    Prom->>Proxy: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token (prometheus-k8s SA)
    activate Proxy

    Note over Proxy: Hardcoded authorizer:<br/>matches SA = system:serviceaccount:<br/>openshift-monitoring:prometheus-k8s<br/>+ GET /metrics → auto-allow

    Note over Proxy: No TokenReview/SAR needed<br/>(hardcoded bypass)

    Proxy->>Upstream: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8081 localhost
    activate Upstream
    Upstream-->>Proxy: Metrics response<br/>(Prometheus format)
    deactivate Upstream
    Proxy-->>Prom: HTTPS metrics response
    deactivate Proxy
